# Radar defense mode. Essentials: two players, three terrritories each.

MaxTeams 2
MinTeams 2
TerritoriesPerTeam 3
RandomTerritories 1

# Custom game mode, big world.
GameMode 6
WorldScale 200

# Cities are irrelevant, so we turn them down as low as we can.
CheckLimits 0
CitiesPerTerritory 1
PopulationPerTerritory 1

# Victory timer, start at 51% so nobody can stall the game by not firing anything.
VictoryTrigger 51
VictoryTimer 120

# No navy, no air force.
ForbidSubmarine 1
ForbidCarrier 1
ForbidBattleship 1
ForbidAirbase 1

# Start up with the players only able to place radars and radar sharing on.
ForbidSilo 1
RadarSharing 3

# Talk about the rules.
WaitClient
WaitSeconds 2
Say Hi there. This is Radar Defense (invented by RC, I think). Rules:
WaitSeconds 5
Say Everyone gets three territorie, world scale will be 200% for LOTS of units.
WaitSeconds 5
Say During Defcon 5, you can only place radars. Your will see each other's placements.
WaitSeconds 5
Say During Decon 4, you can only place silos. Their placements will be secret.
WaitSeconds 5
Say The goal then is to have more radars surviving than your enemy. The displayed scores are irrelevant.
WaitSeconds 5
Say The proper settings will be applied once both players ready up.

WaitStart
Say You now can place only radars. Good Luck!

# At defcon 4, we disable radar sharing and allow only silo placment.
WaitDefcon 4
ForbidSilo 0
ForbidRadar 1
RadarSharing 0
Say You now can place only silos.

# At defcon 3, we fast forward to shortly before defcon 1, nothing can happen there anyway.
WaitDefcon 3
GameSpeed 4
WaitDefcon 2
WaitGameSeconds 590
GameSpeed 0
WaitDefcon 1
Say Get those radars down!
